A man dressed as a woman robbed a service station in Taylors Hill last month . 
  A 23-year-old man was arrested on Thursday and charged with one count of armed robbery . 
  He allegedly confronted a female cashier with a homemade machine gun . 
  He was wearing a blonde wig, red lipstick and a mauve skirt . 
  The man allegedly held up the store with a fake firearm and demanded money from the till . 
 